cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the generation of HDR images from LDR images using deep CNNs. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves graphics and visualization (cs.GR), multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) due to the use of deep learning techniques and data-driven approaches.
